room_title: Escape room "Photoshop Panic" by Unravel Escape Rooms in New York
room_description:
You have been personally invited to a private viewing of Miss. Shutter’s vintage photography shop. However, the promise of a photographer’s paradise fades away as suspicion and worry begin to set in.
Why is nobody else here? What is Miss Shutter’s true identity? Will you find out her true name before she reveals her true intention for you? To uncover the dark truth and get out, perhaps you’ll need to look at the shop room through a different lens…
